I'M LEAVING THE CAFETERIA,
AND I'M WALKING PAST A TABLE,

14:57.567 --> 15:00.267
AND THIS HORRIBLE MAN
USES THE MOST VILE WORD

15:00.300 --> 15:02.933
IN THE ENGLISH LANGUAGE
TO REFER TO A BLACK PERSON.

15:02.967 --> 15:04.667
AND I WENT
INTO A BLIND RAGE.

15:04.700 --> 15:07.200
AND I LEFT THERE AND I WENT
TO THE OPERATING ROOM,

15:07.233 --> 15:10.333
AND I MADE
THIS TERRIBLE MISTAKE,
FOR WHICH I'M SO SORRY.

15:10.367 --> 15:11.733
DO YOU KNOW WHO
THIS MAN WAS?

15:11.767 --> 15:13.400
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHO HE WAS.

15:13.433 --> 15:16.067
HE WAS JUST
A DESPICABLE BALD MAN.

15:16.067 --> 15:17.767
- BALD?
- YE

15:17.800 --> 15:20.467
