AWFUL.

15:34.067 --> 15:35.667
"S..."

15:35.700 --> 15:38.300
"SITTER"?
"SITTING"?

15:40.067 --> 15:42.067
( rapping on door )

15:43.067 --> 15:44.667
( sighs )

15:47.333 --> 15:49.067
LOOK AT HIM!

15:49.067 --> 15:50.867
- LOOK AT HIM!
- WHAT THE FUCK?

15:50.900 --> 15:52.767
- I'M BALD!
- YOU LIKE THIS LOOK?

15:52.800 --> 15:55.067
- HE HAD A BEAUTIFUL
FULL HEAD OF HAIR...
- I'M BALD!

15:55.067 --> 15:57.300
...A MANE THAT I LOVED
AND NOW HE LOOKS LIKE YOU!

15:57.333 --> 15:59.167
- LOOK AT ME!
- WHAT HAPPENED?

15:59.200 --> 16:01.367
- HOW DID THAT HAPPEN?
- YOU DID IT!

16:01.400 --> 16:02.900
- I DID IT?
- YOU DID IT! YES!

16:02.933 --> 16:05.700
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
- YOU TRAUMATIZED THE DOCTOR!

16:05.733 --> 16:09.967
HE DESCRIBED YOU.
HE SAID, "BALD, GLASSES."
YOU SAID SOME RACIAL SLUR

16:10.067 --> 16:11.933
AND YOU TRAUMATIZEDTHE DOCTOR.

16:11.967 --> 16:13.767
- AND HE CAME IN
ALL FLUMMOXED...
- WHAT DID YOU DO?

16:13.800 --> 16:15.967
