HIS FUCKING HEAD!

16:16.067 --> 16:17.600
THERE'S NOTHING WRONG
WITH BEING BALD!

16:17.633 --> 16:19.667
- SURE THERE IS!
- YES, THERE IS, LARRY!

16:19.700 --> 16:22.067
- LOOK AT YOU!
- YOU SAID YOU WOULDN'T
CARE IF YOU WERE BALD!

16:22.067 --> 16:23.700
YEAH, IN 40 YEARS!
NOT FUCKING TODAY!

16:23.733 --> 16:25.733
BECAUSE HE KNEW IT WAS
NEVER GONNA HAPPEN!

16:25.767 --> 16:27.933
- NOT OVERNIGHT!
- YOURS IS GONNA GROW BACK.
MINE ISN'T!

16:27.967 --> 16:29.667
THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU KNOW WHAT?
CURSE ON YOU!

16:29.700 --> 16:32.067
MINE'S GONNA
GROW BACK. YOURS ISN'T!
YOU DESERVE IT!

16:32.067 --> 16:33.900
Susie:
WHAT DID YOU SAY
TO THAT DOCTOR?

16:33.933 --> 16:36.167
HERE'S WHAT HAPPENED, OKAY?
HERE'S WHAT HAPPENED.

16:36.200 --> 16:39.367
I WAS IN THE CAFETERIA.
I WAS HAVING LUNCH
WITH DR. FLOMM.

16:39.400 --> 16:41.633
OKAY? WHAT--
YOU KNOW, IT WAS PRETTY...

16:41.667 --> 16:44.433
BY THE WAY, CAN YOU
INTERPRET THIS-- THIS NOTE?

16:44.467 --> 16:46.500
OH, NOBODY GIVES A SHIT
ABOUT YOUR NOTE!

16:46.533 --> 16:47.900
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
- HUH?

16:47.933 --> 16:50.233
OKAY, SO I WENT
TO THE MEN'S ROOM.

16:50.267 --> 16:52.633
I'M IN THE STALL.
THERE'S THIS GUY,

16:52.667 --> 16:54.167
AN UNBELIEVABLE
ASSHOLE.

16:54.200 --> 16:56.267
HE'S TALKING
ON HIS CELL PHONE
TO HIS FRIEND.

16:56.300 --> 16:58.933
HE'S VERY UPSET
BECAUSE THEY HAD TO
MOVE SOME FURNITURE.

16:58.967 --> 17:00.800
HE SAYS TO HIS FRIEND,
"I HURT MY HAND

17:00.833 --> 17:03.367
- BECAUSE THIS
300-LB NIGGER IS--"
- WHAT'D YOU SAY?

17:03.400 --> 17:05.400
- WHAT?
- WHAT DID YOU JUST SAY?

17:05.433 --> 17:08.167
- OH NO NO, I--
- DID I JUST HEAR THE WORD
