- HOW YOU GONNA SAY
NIGGER, MAN?
- NO NO!

17:21.067 --> 17:22.667
IS THAT HOW YOU
FEEL ABOUT US?

17:22.700 --> 17:24.900
THAT WE A BUNCH
OF NIGGERS UP IN HERE?

17:24.933 --> 17:27.933
- I WAS QUOTING SOMEBODY.
- LET'S GET OUT OF HERE!
I WANNA GO!

17:27.967 --> 17:30.600
WHAT IS ALL THIS
FUSSING AND CUSSING
GOING ON UP IN HERE?

17:30.633 --> 17:32.300
