CALLED US NIGGER.

17:32.333 --> 17:33.633
- NIGGER?
- Both: NIGGER!

17:33.667 --> 17:36.167
- NO, LET ME EXPLAIN!
- YOU LOST YOUR DAMN MIND NOW!

17:36.200 --> 17:39.800
FIRST, YOU'RE GONNA BE RUBBING
ALL UP AGAINST ME, THEN WHACKING
OFF IN THE DAMN CAR!

