- THIS THE LAST STRAW.
WE OUT THIS BITCH.
- THAT'S IT.

17:53.133 --> 17:54.400
- WE OUT THIS BITCH!
- OUT.

17:54.433 --> 17:56.233
- WHERE YOU GONNA GO?
- WE DON'T KNOW.

17:56.267 --> 17:58.500
