- THANK YOU!

18:01.900 --> 18:04.567
FUCK YOU, LARRY,
WIT' YOUR MONKEY ASS!

18:04.600 --> 18:06.400
Auntie Rae:
DARYL! KEYSHA!

18:06.433 --> 18:08.333
- WE GETTIN'
THE HELL OUTTA HERE.
