18:12.400 --> 18:14.600
FUCK YOU, LARRY!

18:14.633 --> 18:16.533
PEACE!

18:20.100 --> 18:22.333
WELL, LOOK, I--
I THINK THAT

18:22.367 --> 18:25.633
YOU'RE LIMITING YOURSELF
BY JUST DOING COMEDIES.

18:25.667 --> 18:27.533
- RIGHT.
- YOU CAN DO IT
IN YOUR SLEEP.

18:27.567 --> 18:29.067
LET'S SHOW PEOPLE MORE.

18:29.067 --> 18:31.233
WHY CAN'T YOU WIN
AN ACADEMY AWARD?

18:31.267 --> 18:33.800
