ANYTHING YOU WANT TO DO.

18:33.833 --> 18:36.433
WE JUST GOTTA PUSH 'EM
IN THE RIGHT DIRECTION, MAN.

18:36.467 --> 18:38.367
- YEAH.
- THAT'S IT.

18:38.400 --> 18:40.833
- I DIDN'T JUST FALL
OFF THE MELON TRUCK.
