19:10.400 --> 19:12.633
- WHAT?
- DOESN'T WANT
TO WORK WITH ME.

19:12.667 --> 19:15.967
- ARE YOU KIDDING?
- DOESN'T FEEL IT'S RIGHT.

19:16.067 --> 19:17.767
- HE CALLED YOU?
- YEAH.

19:17.800 --> 19:19.500
