TO MEET WITH ME.

19:57.067 --> 19:59.667
THEY WANT TO TALK AND--
AND GO OVER MY BILL.

19:59.700 --> 20:02.500
"GO OVER MY BILL."
I'M GONNA SUE THESE
MOTHERFUCKERS.

20:02.533 --> 20:04.800
- THAT'S IT!
THAT'S FUCKING IT!
- RIGHT, GOOD FOR YOU.

20:04.833 --> 20:06.933
THIS BLOWS.
HOW DO YOU DEAL WITH IT?

20:06.967 --> 20:10.633
YOU JUST GET USED TO IT.
AND I GET SUPPORT
FROM MY BALD BROTHERS.

20:10.667 --> 20:12.833
- THERE'S, LIKE, MEETINGS?
- THERE'S NO MEETINGS,

20:12.867 --> 20:15.067
BUT WE SEE EACH OTHER
ON THE STREET, WE NOD.

20:15.100 --> 20:17.900
- WE'LL GIVE A THUMBS UP.
- YEAH.

20:17.933 --> 20:20.967
YOU KNOW WHAT?
WE LOVE EACH OTHER,
ME AND MY BALD BROTHERS.

20:21.000 --> 20:22.933
STILL OBSESSED
WITH THAT NOTE, HUH?

20:22.967 --> 20:25.700
I-- I'VE ASKED
10 PEOPLE.

20:25.733 --> 20:28.100
EXCUSE ME, COULD YOU
DO ME A FAVOR?

20:28.133 --> 20:31.100
I CAN'T READ THIS.
COULD YOU MAKE OUT
ANY OF THAT HANDWRITING?

20:31.133 --> 20:32.400
- THIS FROM A DOCTOR?
- YEAH.

20:32.433 --> 20:34.367
TAKE IT
TO A PHARMACIST.

20:37.200 --> 20:38.833
- WHAT A GREAT IDEA.
- YEAH.

20:38.867 --> 20:41.067
THEY'RE THE ONLY
ONES WHO CAN MAKE OUT
A DOCTOR'S HANDWRITING.

20:41.100 --> 20:42.567
YEAH, GO!

20:45.133 --> 20:47.033
- OH, HI.
- HI.

20:47.067 --> 20:49.767
RRY DAVID.
I DROPPED OFF A PRESCRIPTION
THE OTHER DAY.

20:49.800 --> 20:51.467
- AH YES YES, HERE WE GO.
- YEAH.

20:51.500 --> 20:54.333
ACTUALLY, I WANT
TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT
SOMETHING ELSE TOO.

20:54.367 --> 20:56.467
I'M GOING OUT
WITH A DOCTOR,

20:56.500 --> 20:58.500
AND SHE WROTE ME
THIS NOTE,

20:58.533 --> 21:00.767
- AND I CANNOT...
- AND YOU CAN'T READ IT.

21:00.800 --> 21:02.800
I CAN'T READ IT!
IT'S UNBELIEVABLE.

21:02.833 --> 21:04.800
- NOBODY CAN!
- YES.

21:04.833 --> 21:06.600
SO SOMEBODY SUGGESTED
A PHARMACIST,

21:06.633 --> 21:08.533
'CAUSE NOBODY CAN
DECIPHER THIS THING.

21:08.567 --> 21:10.333
LET ME--
LET ME TAKE A SHOT.

21:10.367 --> 21:12.367
YOU'RE MY ONLY HOPE.

21:12.400 --> 21:16.067
"LARRY, HAD A GREAT TIME
LAST NIGHT.

21:16.067 --> 21:19.800
